Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.89,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對聖母瑪利亞 保·密·哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.56,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.13,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.41,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了呢  祐巳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.17,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:26.38,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想給姐姐打個電話為今天的事致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.90,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻不知道會是哪一位來接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:31.20,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不是那麼輕易就能打出去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.80,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是福澤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.09,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯而給掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:43.27,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉著一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.45,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.90,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天就能再與最喜歡的姐姐相見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.20,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然今天是如此愉快的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.85,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天也一定會是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.47,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是我與姐姐的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:12.47,zhengwentcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  姐姐
